abstract: How the protesters are planning to deal with forecast of snow; what Google has found out about the relative interest in Occupy Wall Street and the Tea Party movement; the New York Civil Liberties Union sets up a table in Zuccotti Park; and more.
snippet: How the protesters are planning to deal with forecast of snow; what Google has found out about the relative interest in Occupy Wall Street and the Tea Party movement; the New York Civil Liberties Union sets up a table in Zuccotti Park; and more.
lead_paragraph: With snow in the forecast and Zuccotti Park newly bereft of gas generators protesters are stocking up on Mylar sleeping bags and bike generators. [City Room, Dawn Hoag via Twitter, Young Manhattanite]
